{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mysterious creatures are attacking the empire! The pharaoh needs you to build a defense to defeat them.   You must channel the divine power to retake your temples and build towers.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Place towers and connect them to the palace via power lines</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275770/extras/ObeliskPowered.gif?t=1734358515\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Towers need to be connected to your power line network to work. After every wave you get more power crystals to extend your network.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Upgrade towers to improve their abilities<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275770/extras/TowerUpgradesAnimated.gif?t=1734358515\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After a tower is built its full potential is not yet reached. You can upgrade it up to three times to improve its range, strength, and speed.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Retake temples to gain extra resources each wave</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275770/extras/TempleAnimated.gif?t=1734358515\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The temples were captured by enemies, so you need to cleanse them by connecting them to your power line network. After some time their blue flame will light up again and they will supply you with additional resources.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3275770?t=1734358515","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3275770?t=1734358515","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275770/49c1b889ded318fd429ebbf4e91a40842776d755/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734358515","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/s